If you're sitting there
thinking, well, yeah,

00:13:22.420 --> 00:13:24.270
Doug, it sounds great,
but how do you do it,

00:13:24.270 --> 00:13:27.280
or what does that really mean,
or I agree, or I disagree,

00:13:27.280 --> 00:13:27.780
let me know.

00:13:27.780 --> 00:13:30.060
Does anybody have any
questions-- any clarification

00:13:30.060 --> 00:13:31.230
necessary at this time?

00:13:31.230 --> 00:13:32.430
We've got mic runners.

